### ===================================
### SECTION 7: CORE BANK API DIRECT TESTS
### ===================================

### 7.1 Process Transaction with Idempotency (CoreBank)
POST {{coreBankApiUrl}}/api/transactions/process
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fromAccount": "{{account1}}",
  "toAccount": "{{account2}}",
  "amount": 200.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "idempotencyKey": "corebank-txn-001"
}

### 7.2 Retry Same Transaction (Should be idempotent)
POST {{coreBankApiUrl}}/api/transactions/process
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fromAccount": "{{account1}}",
  "toAccount": "{{account2}}",
  "amount": 200.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "idempotencyKey": "corebank-txn-001"
}

### 7.3 Validate Account (CoreBank)
POST {{coreBankApiUrl}}/api/accounts/validate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountNumber": "{{account1}}"
}

### 7.4 Check Inbox Messages (CoreBank)
GET {{coreBankApiUrl}}/api/inbox

